BUG				Galactic Bloodshed		     BUG


NAME
   bug [0] -- make a bug report

SYNTAX
    bug <message>

DESCRIPTION
  	This command will send a bug report via internet email to the host
(god) of the game.  It assures prompt action of possible bugs.  If you
find a bug, please use this mechanism to alert the god.


SEE ALSO
   page, communications
